[SN]TITLE[SN]
Bury: Nathan Delfouneso, Cian Bolger and Chris Neal join on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Bury have signed Blackburn striker Nathan Delfouneso, Southend defender Cian Bolger and Port Vale goalkeeper Chris Neal on loan.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Former Aston Villa man Delfouneso, 24, has joined until 19 April after scoring twice in 16 games for Rovers this term.
Ex-Leicester City trainee Bolger, 24, and keeper Neal, 30, have both agreed to stay until the end of the season.
All three players are available for the Shakers' League One game against Shrewsbury on Saturday.
